1
00:00:00,140 --> 00:00:03,060
=The Crow Princess of Fortune=

2
00:00:03,060 --> 00:00:04,980
=Episode 7=

3
00:00:06,340 --> 00:00:07,900
What's going on?

4
00:00:09,620 --> 00:00:11,419
What's going on? Did you see that just now?

5
00:00:11,420 --> 00:00:12,139
You...

6
00:00:12,140 --> 00:00:12,819
Xiao Heng!

7
00:00:12,820 --> 00:00:13,499
You...

8
00:00:13,500 --> 00:00:16,060
How dare you assault someone
in the imperial hall!

9
00:00:16,180 --> 00:00:17,939
Father, did you see that?

10
00:00:17,940 --> 00:00:19,499
He openly attacked people

11
00:00:19,500 --> 00:00:20,499
right in

12
00:00:20,500 --> 00:00:21,780
the imperial hall!

13
00:00:21,980 --> 00:00:24,419
Father, you must punish him properly!

14
00:00:24,420 --> 00:00:25,900
Your Highness,

15
00:00:26,300 --> 00:00:28,379
I was saving you.

16
00:00:28,380 --> 00:00:30,140
What?

17
00:00:30,500 --> 00:00:33,459
These two officials dared to speak
recklessly about the royal family

18
00:00:33,460 --> 00:00:34,779
right in front of Father.

19
00:00:34,780 --> 00:00:35,939
According to Tianxuan law,

20
00:00:35,940 --> 00:00:38,060
what crime should they be charged with?

21
00:00:38,260 --> 00:00:39,380
We...

22
00:00:39,460 --> 00:00:41,900
- We wouldn't dare!
- We wouldn't dare!

23
00:00:42,180 --> 00:00:43,300
Father,

24
00:00:43,700 --> 00:00:45,940
what I struck down wasn't their hats,

25
00:00:46,060 --> 00:00:48,260
but their disrespect toward you.

26
00:00:49,520 --> 00:00:51,000
(Father is amazing.)

27
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:52,240
(He was clearly hitting people,)

28
00:00:52,240 --> 00:00:53,960
(yet somehow he made it
sound so righteous.)

29
00:00:53,960 --> 00:00:54,660
You...

30
00:00:54,740 --> 00:00:56,380
You're twisting the truth!

31
00:00:57,100 --> 00:00:58,499
Suisui,

32
00:00:58,500 --> 00:01:00,379
they were speaking badly about you.

33
00:01:00,380 --> 00:01:02,219
Do you want to say something yourself?

34
00:01:02,220 --> 00:01:03,380
Of course.

35
00:01:13,820 --> 00:01:18,859
Well, I didn't expect all of you

36
00:01:18,860 --> 00:01:20,780
to have such tiny hearts,

37
00:01:20,940 --> 00:01:23,499
but such huge scandals.

38
00:01:23,500 --> 00:01:26,380
I don't even know where to start.

39
00:01:26,680 --> 00:01:27,579
Let's start with mine.

40
00:01:27,580 --> 00:01:28,499
Your youngest son

41
00:01:28,500 --> 00:01:30,900
looks exactly like
Official Wang across the hall.

42
00:01:31,180 --> 00:01:32,499
Sir,

43
00:01:32,500 --> 00:01:34,459
other people's backyards catch fire,

44
00:01:34,460 --> 00:01:36,779
but your backyard
could open a whole racetrack.

45
00:01:36,780 --> 00:01:39,780
Nothing but green fields everywhere.

46
00:01:40,220 --> 00:01:42,559
Every month on the fifteenth,
your wife goes to

47
00:01:42,560 --> 00:01:45,460
the Guanyin Temple
in the east of the city.

48
00:01:45,500 --> 00:01:48,939
And every single time, Official Wang
just happens to run into her there.

49
00:01:48,940 --> 00:01:50,620
Isn't that right?

50
00:01:52,300 --> 00:01:54,300
Wang Dazhen!

51
00:01:54,380 --> 00:01:56,819
Well done, Wang.

52
00:01:56,820 --> 00:01:58,579
Didn't know you had it in you.

53
00:01:58,580 --> 00:01:59,820
That's not true!

54
00:02:00,380 --> 00:02:01,419
As for you,

55
00:02:01,420 --> 00:02:03,379
not only are you keeping a mistress,

56
00:02:03,380 --> 00:02:05,660
you also embezzled
disaster relief funds.

57
00:02:05,860 --> 00:02:09,019
Didn't you bribe Official Li?

58
00:02:09,020 --> 00:02:10,179
The little mice said

59
00:02:10,180 --> 00:02:11,959
they saw you

60
00:02:11,960 --> 00:02:14,579
bribing Official Li last night.

61
00:02:14,580 --> 00:02:17,379
Nonsense! We're upright
and incorruptible!

62
00:02:17,380 --> 00:02:18,699
Utter nonsense!

63
00:02:18,700 --> 00:02:20,040
Your Majesty, please see the truth!

64
00:02:20,040 --> 00:02:21,500
Upright and incorruptible?

65
00:02:22,060 --> 00:02:24,420
You're filthy rich.

66
00:02:24,580 --> 00:02:26,379
I've known it all along.

67
00:02:26,380 --> 00:02:28,499
Official Zhang,
you're keeping a mistress.

68
00:02:28,500 --> 00:02:30,320
Official Li,
you're running loan shark schemes.

69
00:02:30,320 --> 00:02:31,480
Don't think we don't know.

70
00:02:31,480 --> 00:02:32,820
You're framing us!

71
00:02:32,940 --> 00:02:34,540
You're framing us!

72
00:02:42,980 --> 00:02:44,580
I'll kill you!

73
00:02:54,620 --> 00:02:57,579
What a waste for all this stuff
to fall on the floor.

74
00:02:57,580 --> 00:03:01,239
Let me help keep it safe for you.

75
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:03,360
(Chenhua Palace)

76
00:03:05,980 --> 00:03:07,100
Mother,

77
00:03:09,580 --> 00:03:11,619
I was bullied, Mother.

78
00:03:11,620 --> 00:03:12,499
Oh my,

79
00:03:12,500 --> 00:03:13,619
my precious son.

80
00:03:13,620 --> 00:03:15,180
What happened to you?

81
00:03:16,420 --> 00:03:17,780
It was Xiao Heng.

82
00:03:18,100 --> 00:03:20,100
And that wild girl he picked up.

83
00:03:20,300 --> 00:03:22,860
They joined forces
to swindle me out of my money

84
00:03:22,940 --> 00:03:24,460
and even tricked me out of my clothes.

85
00:03:24,900 --> 00:03:26,099
I went to complain to Father,

86
00:03:26,100 --> 00:03:27,179
Father...

87
00:03:27,180 --> 00:03:28,819
Not only did Father not punish them,

88
00:03:28,820 --> 00:03:31,900
he even granted that wild girl
the title of princess.

89
00:03:32,860 --> 00:03:35,179
Mother, look at my face.

90
00:03:35,180 --> 00:03:37,419
Oh, you've gained weight.

91
00:03:37,420 --> 00:03:39,220
You've gotten rounder.

92
00:03:39,580 --> 00:03:40,459
No.

93
00:03:40,460 --> 00:03:42,740
I got stung and swollen, Mother.

94
00:03:42,820 --> 00:03:44,019
Alright.

95
00:03:44,020 --> 00:03:47,500
Mother, I just can't let this go.

96
00:03:47,580 --> 00:03:48,619
Stop crying.

97
00:03:48,620 --> 00:03:50,500
Alright.

98
00:03:50,980 --> 00:03:51,939
Tomorrow,

99
00:03:51,940 --> 00:03:53,419
I'll summon them into the palace

100
00:03:53,420 --> 00:03:55,500
and help you vent this anger, alright?

101
00:03:55,620 --> 00:03:56,259
Mother!

102
00:03:56,260 --> 00:03:57,539
Stop crying.

103
00:03:57,540 --> 00:04:00,220
Alright, don't cry anymore.

104
00:04:00,740 --> 00:04:02,519
There now.

105
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:04,100
Good boy, no more crying.

106
00:04:05,720 --> 00:04:07,040
(Invitation)

107
00:04:09,380 --> 00:04:11,380
Tomorrow's palace banquet.

108
00:04:11,420 --> 00:04:14,939
Prince Jing and his daughter
are invited to the palace gathering.

109
00:04:14,940 --> 00:04:18,419
Consort Shu?

110
00:04:18,420 --> 00:04:20,699
Your Highness, we absolutely
cannot attend this banquet.

111
00:04:20,700 --> 00:04:21,859
That's right, Your Highness.

112
00:04:21,860 --> 00:04:24,289
Whenever Consort Shu has something good,
she never remembers you.

113
00:04:24,289 --> 00:04:25,240
Every time she summons you,

114
00:04:25,240 --> 00:04:26,680
it's either to make you take
the blame for the Crown Prince

115
00:04:26,680 --> 00:04:28,120
or to scold you for drawing
too much attention.

116
00:04:28,140 --> 00:04:30,099
A palace banquet?
This is clearly a trap.

117
00:04:30,100 --> 00:04:30,819
What bad luck.

118
00:04:30,820 --> 00:04:32,100
I'll burn it for you.

119
00:04:32,740 --> 00:04:34,220
This banquet,

120
00:04:34,540 --> 00:04:36,660
I must attend.

121
00:04:36,700 --> 00:04:37,500
Huh?

122
00:04:38,100 --> 00:04:39,820
Can't you all tell?

123
00:04:41,100 --> 00:04:42,539
My daughter

124
00:04:42,540 --> 00:04:43,900
loves attending banquets.

125
00:04:58,000 --> 00:05:01,319
♪Little lucky star,
twinkling with a wink at me♪

126
00:05:01,320 --> 00:05:05,159
♪Every Chinese New Year day brings
the luckiest fortune slip♪

127
00:05:05,160 --> 00:05:08,679
♪The God of Wealth favors me,
the Matchmaker ties red strings for me♪

128
00:05:08,680 --> 00:05:11,640
♪With firecrackers going off,
good things keep coming one after another♪

129
00:05:12,520 --> 00:05:16,159
♪Make a wish on the very first day
of the Chinese New Year♪

130
00:05:16,160 --> 00:05:19,920
♪By the second day,
my belly's already round♪

131
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:23,319
♪Always talking about dieting,
but the chub never disappears♪

132
00:05:23,320 --> 00:05:27,360
♪Good food brings joy
and happiness every single day♪

133
00:05:32,960 --> 00:05:36,639
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
every year is filled with joy♪

134
00:05:36,640 --> 00:05:40,279
♪I'm bringing blessings to everyone♪

135
00:05:40,280 --> 00:05:43,999
♪Hands clasped together in greeting♪

136
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:47,639
♪May every family be sweet and happy♪

137
00:05:47,640 --> 00:05:51,319
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
may everything go your way♪

138
00:05:51,320 --> 00:05:53,239
♪Endlessly flowing♪

139
00:05:53,240 --> 00:05:59,440
♪Good fortune♪
